[[费尔南多·托雷斯|费尔南多·托雷斯]]是已退役的前[[西班牙国家足球队|西班牙]][[足球|足球]]运动员，从2003年的国家队处子秀到2014年的最后一场比赛，他代表国家队共出场110次，攻入38球。截至2019年，他是国家队历史第三射手，进球数仅次于[[大卫·比利亚|大卫·比利亚]]（59球）和[[劳尔·冈萨雷斯|劳尔]]（44球）。西班牙在他进球时从未输过比赛<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.goal.com/en/news/2898/euro-2012/2012/06/17/3180025/spains-lucky-charm-when-torres-scores-la-roja-never-lose |title=Spain's lucky charm: When Torres scores, La Roja never lose |last=Pinero |first=Alberto |website=Goal.com |publisher=Perform Group |date=2012-06-17 |accessdate=2018-04-04 |archive-date=2019-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427134807/https://www.goal.com/en/news/2898/euro-2012/2012/06/17/3180025/spains-lucky-charm-when-torres-scores-la-roja-never-lose |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

托雷斯曾代表西班牙参加过不同级别的青年队比赛，在2003年9月6日对阵[[葡萄牙国家足球队|葡萄牙]]的比赛中首次登场，并在2004年4月28日对阵[[意大利国家足球队|意大利]]的[[热身赛|热身赛]]中打入个人首粒进球<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/euro_2004/spain/players_to_watch/3594045.stm |title=Fernando Torres |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2014-05-25 |accessdate=2018-04-04 |archive-date=2008-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080102124207/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/euro_2004/spain/players_to_watch/3594045.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=one>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2004/apr/29/newsstory.sport11 |title=Italians salute Baggio cameo: Vieri equalises Torres strike |last=McCarra |first=Kevin |newspaper=The Guardian |location=London |date=2004-04-29 |accessdate=2016-12-22 |archive-date=2019-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427134756/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2004/apr/29/newsstory.sport11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[2006年国际足联世界杯|2006年国际足联世界杯]][[2006年國際足協世界盃外圍賽|预选赛]]期间，托雷斯出场11次攻入7球，帮助西班牙队成功晋级世界杯<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fifa.com/fifa-tournaments/players-coaches/people=183864/index.html |title=Fernando Torres |publisher=FIFA |accessdate=2016-12-21 |archive-date=2018-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180624150345/https://www.fifa.com/fifa-tournaments/players-coaches/people=183864/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在本届世界杯上，他打进3球，在对阵[[突尼斯国家足球队|突尼斯]]时打进两球，西班牙在八分之一决赛被[[法国国家足球队|法国]]淘汰<ref name=Tun>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4853264.stm |title=Spain 3–1 Tunisia |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2006-06-19 |accessdate=2018-04-04 |archive-date=2007-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071002082452/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/world_cup_2006/4853264.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在两年后的[[2008年欧洲足球锦标赛|2008年欧洲足球锦标赛]]上，托雷斯在对阵[[德国国家足球队|德国]]的决赛第33分钟打入制胜一球，结束了西班牙44年无冠的尴尬纪录<ref name=E08>{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/columnists/henrywinter/2304399/Fernando-Torres-strike-wins-Euro-2008-for-Spain-to-leave-Germany-empty-handed.html |title=Fernando Torres' strike wins Euro 2008 for Spain to leave Germany empty handed |last=Winter |first=Henry |newspaper=The Daily Telegraph |location=London |date=2008-06-30 |accessdate=2018-04-04 |archive-date=2019-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427135339/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/columnists/henrywinter/2304399/Fernando-Torres-strike-wins-Euro-2008-for-Spain-to-leave-Germany-empty-handed.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

夺得2008年欧洲杯冠军帮助西班牙以欧洲冠军的身份晋级[[2009年国际足联联合会杯|2009年国际足联联合会杯]]，这也是[[2010年南非世界杯|2010年南非世界杯]]的预热赛。托雷斯在联合会杯上共打入三球，在6月14日西班牙5:0战胜[[新西兰国家足球队|新西兰]]的比赛中上演了[[帽子戏法|帽子戏法]]<ref name=CC>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2009/jun/14/south-africa-iraq-confederations-cup |title=Fernando Torres's hat-trick stains All Whites |newspaper=The Guardian |location=London |date=2009-06-14 |accessdate=2016-12-22 |archive-date=2019-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427135336/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2009/jun/14/south-africa-iraq-confederations-cup |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他在开场11分钟即打入3球，创造了比赛历史上最快的帽子戏法记录。托雷斯在一年后举行的世界杯上未能收获进球，但他作为世界杯冠军成员，在[[2010年国际足联世界杯决赛|决赛]]中以{{tsl|en|Substitute (association football)||替补}}身份得到了上场机会<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/y=2010/m=7/news=iniesta-puts-spain-top-the-world-1272241.html |title=Iniesta puts Spain on top of the world |publisher=FIFA |date=2010-07-11 |accessdate=2018-04-04 |archive-date=2018-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180404170955/https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/y=2010/m=7/news=iniesta-puts-spain-top-the-world-1272241.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年，托雷斯入选了[[2012年欧洲足球锦标赛|2012年欧洲足球锦标赛]]国家队大名单，并凭借3粒进球获得了欧洲杯金靴奖。他在对阵[[爱尔兰国家足球队|爱尔兰]]的比赛中梅开二度，在决赛对阵意大利的比赛中打进第三球，最终帮助队伍4:0取胜。这粒进球也是他在欧洲杯决赛的第二个进球<ref name=E12>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/18670818 |title=Euro 2012: Spain striker Fernando Torres wins Golden Boot award |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2012-07-02 |accessdate=2018-04-04 |archive-date=2019-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190510080945/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/18670818 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。次年，托雷斯在[[2013年国际足联联合会杯|2013年国际足联联合会杯]]上共打入5球并再次获得金靴奖。在与[[塔希提足球代表队|塔希提]]的比赛中，托雷斯上演了大四喜<ref>{{cite news |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/blogs/soccer-dirty-tackle/fernando-torres-wins-another-golden-boot-award-understandably-040203642.html |title=Fernando Torres wins another Golden Boot award, is understandably less than excited about it |last=Peck |first=Brooks |publisher=Yahoo! Sports |date=2013-07-01 |accessdate=2016-12-22 |archive-date=2019-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427140332/https://sports.yahoo.com/blogs/soccer-dirty-tackle/fernando-torres-wins-another-golden-boot-award-understandably-040203642.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=CC2>{{cite news |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/international/confederations-cup-fernando-torres-scores-four-despite-missing-a-penalty-as-spain-crush-tahiti-10-0-8668168.html |title=Confederations Cup: Fernando Torres scores four (despite missing a penalty) as Spain crush Tahiti 10–0 |newspaper=The Independent |location=London |date=2013-06-21 |accessdate=2016-12-22 |archive-date=2019-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427141105/https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/international/confederations-cup-fernando-torres-scores-four-despite-missing-a-penalty-as-spain-crush-tahiti-10-0-8668168.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。随后，他入选了[[2014年巴西世界杯|2014年巴西世界杯]]国家队大名单，并在小组赛3:0战胜[[澳大利亚国家足球队|澳大利亚]]的比赛中攻入一球。不过，这对西班牙来说是一场{{le|无关痛痒的比赛|Dead rubber}}，因为他们已经确定被淘汰出局<ref name=WC14>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/23/australia-spain-world-cup-2014-group-b-match-report |title=David Villa helps Spain salvage some pride with victory over Australia |last=Lowe |first=Sid |newspaper=The Guardian |location=London |date=2014-06-23 |accessdate=2018-04-04 |archive-date=2019-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427140330/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/23/australia-spain-world-cup-2014-group-b-match-report |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在托雷斯的38个国际比赛进球中，10个来自于热身赛中；8个来自于联合会杯；7个来自于世界杯预选赛；5个来自于欧洲杯；欧洲杯预选赛和世界杯各有4球<ref>{{NFT player |id=6219 |name=Torres, Fernando |accessdate=2018-04-04}}</ref>。

